narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Continuation of GMAN 130. The course was more in depth than the prior course and required more work. I would recommend this course.
The class was pretty similar to L3 and pretty comprehensive.
I think I enjoyed this the most of the German classes I've taken. We didn't do as much reading as the course description implies, but we had some good discussions and covered some interesting topics.
Yes. The class is thorough and we learned a lot. The variety of reading, writing, speaking, and listening is strong.
